name: Emily Worden
text: Nothing fancy but it doesn't need to be! They are my favorite local pizza spot in vb. The pizza is always delicious

name: Adrian Roth
text: Ordered online and paid for it. Went to the shop and they said I didn't so I paid again. Got home and checked and Yep, I sure did pay. Checked my bank and Yep, they sure charged me twice. Called the store- thought it'd be an easy fix but â€¦More

name: Christopher Karsanac
text: Always my goto pizza place.  I live near this, and, therefore, near YNot.  And I honestly prefer their pizza to YNot.  I love the crust and the sauce.  Never had a bad pie.  I don't order anything else but the pizza, so I can't comment on the rest of their menu.

name: Kash
text: Pizza is always good people are friendly inside and the delivery guy we usually get the same guy lol reasonable price could use more deals or coupons sometimes.

name: Gabriela Ziad
text: Decided to give this place a try and I was very disappointed to waste my money here. I basically traded money for rubbish. They get one star because the salad was the only okay thing, we ordered wings and pizza. Never again.

name: Wendy Zanabria
text: Ordered pizza and it never showed up and never got a phone call from the driver. Do not recommend them.

name: Jesse Geitzmuni's Channel
text: Best pizza in the area! Quick delivery too.

name: greg smith
text: Best pizza ever greatt people love this place

name: Darryous Saunders
text: Fight was going on with employees while i was there.

name: Not Buying
text: Mediocre pizza.  Just like any other "chain".  They do deliver late though.

name: Cleaning Guy'z Company Inc.
text: This been third time I visited the place and they don't wash there hands enough for me. This is the last time I come to this location.
